    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Ujjivan Small Finance Bank Holdings Services. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Credit Analyst to strengthen our Pimpri-Chinchwad-based team.\n\nAbout Ujjivan Small Finance Bank Holdings Services:\nUjjivan Small Finance Bank Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pimpri-Chinchwad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ujjivan Small Finance Bank Holdings Services!",
